<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakava
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rusaṁbulu 1271 nēṭi vīrādivīra naranārasiṁhyadēva vija
<lb n="3" break="no"/>yarājyasaṁvatsaraṁbulu 28 gu śrāhi dhanu śukla Ēkādasi
<lb n="4"/>maṁggaḷavāramunāṁḍu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> kommidēvaṁmmaṁgāru tamaku Ā<supplied reason="omitted">yu</supplied>ṣkā
<lb n="5"/>myārtthamugānu Ubhayadīpālaṁdu paṭṭaṁgalāru <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī divyakō
<lb n="6" break="no"/>lalu reṁḍunu toresiṁgunāku <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Appalavurā Ī torasiṁ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>gāyaku prasāda tu 1 Appamu 1 viḍiya 1 jītamu gaṁḍamā 1
<lb n="8"/>Appalagharāki prasādamu 1 Appamu 1 viḍiyamu 1 jītamu
<lb n="9" break="no"/>gaṁḍamā 1 Īṁdulaku śrīkūrmmanātuni śrībaṁḍāramu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>naṁdu peṭṭina gaṁḍamāḍalu 38 cinnalu 4 Ī dīpana
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ku neĪ nitya Aḍḍa 1 Ī lekkanu peṭina modalu 20 Ī datta
<lb n="12" break="no"/>mu Ācaṁdrārkkamugā celiṁppaṁgalāru Īṁdulaku tirupa
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ti śrīvaiṣṇavarakṣa śrīśrīśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> muppaṁḍru śrīvaiṣṇavanāya
<lb n="14" break="no"/>kulu yettaṁgalāru Okha kuṁḍḍa 1 kaṁstāli nāyaku
<lb n="15" break="no"/>lu muvvurunnu Okha kuṁḍḍa 1 Āppananaṁbiṁgāru maṁcci
<lb n="16" break="no"/>naṁbiṁgāru Okha kuṁḍḍa 1 vinnapamucēyuvāru Āṁ
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ḍammaṁgāru Appallaṁgārunu Okha kuṁḍḍa 1 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

